title: Wurigumula
text: Wurigumula (<a href="Mongolian%20Cyrillic%20alphabet">Mongolian Cyrillic</a>:, <a href="Latin%20script">Latin</a>:Urgamal, ) is a Chinese professional <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who plays as a <a href="Forward%20%28association%20football%29">forward</a> for <a href="Changchun%20Dazhong%20Zhuoyue">Changchun Zhuoyue</a>. She studied in the <a href="Inner%20Mongolia%20Normal%20University">Inner Mongolia Normal University</a>.
